- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper evaluates different log parsers in terms of efficiency and accuracy. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the unstructured nature of logs and the need to parse them into structured data for analysis.
